435
00:27:48,121 --> 00:27:49,511
What goddess?

436
00:27:50,321 --> 00:27:52,791
However, I was ambitious back then.

437
00:27:53,025 --> 00:27:54,306
I wanted to become

438
00:27:54,434 --> 00:27:56,303
