00:28:16,321 --> 00:28:17,541
Listen well.

449
00:28:17,683 --> 00:28:20,073
You are the best trust lawyer to me.

450
00:28:20,729 --> 00:28:23,202
Don't be trapped by the past. It's unnecessary.

451
00:28:24,083 --> 00:28:25,512
